Cepta Help Menu:
    cepta
        Create a new project
        Questions:
            What is your project name?
                Default: myProject
            What type of project is this?
                Choices: Express
            What port shall this project run on?
                Default: 3000
    cepta --help / -h
          Show this help menu
    cepta --version / -v
        Check version of Cepta compared to latest version
    cepta --update / -u
        Update Cepta to the latest version from NPM
  